---
import Layout from "@/layouts/Layout.astro";
import Container from "@/components/container.astro";
import Sectionhead from "@/components/sectionhead.astro";
import { Icon } from "astro-icon/components";
---

<Layout title="EU Authorised Representative | AnichLabs OÜ">
  <Container>
    <Sectionhead>
      <Fragment slot="title">EU Authorised Representative</Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">Formal EU representation under written mandate for non-EU health-tech companies entering the European market.</Fragment>
    </Sectionhead>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-16">
      <div class="bg-red-50 border border-red-100 rounded-2xl p-8">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest text-red-400 mb-3">The Problem</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">Non-EU companies cannot legally place medical devices or high-risk AI in the EU without an EU representative</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">Under EU MDR (2017/745), IVDR (2017/746), and the EU AI Act, any non-EU manufacturer or provider of regulated health-tech products must designate an EU Authorised Representative before they can market or operate in Europe. Without one, your product cannot legally enter the market, no matter how good it is.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-10">
      <div class="rounded-2xl p-8" style="background-color: #EEF2FF; border: 1px solid #C7D2FE;">
        <p class="text-xs font-semibold uppercase tracking-widest mb-3" style="color: #003399">The Solution</p>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-4">A named EU Authorised Representative with healthcare and regulatory expertise</h2>
        <p class="text-slate-600 leading-relaxed">AnichLabs OÜ acts as your formal EU Authorised Representative under written mandate, registered in Estonia (EU). We handle regulatory correspondence, maintain required documentation, and act as the official point of contact for EU authorities, so you can focus on building your product while we handle your EU compliance presence.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8 text-center">What's Included</h2>
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:file-check-alt" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Written Mandate Agreement</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">A legally binding mandate designating AnichLabs OÜ as your EU Authorised Representative under MDR, IVDR, or EU AI Act as applicable.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:map-marker" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">EU Registration</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Registration of your product and representative details with the relevant EU authority (EUDAMED for medical devices, national authorities for AI Act).</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:envelope" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Regulatory Correspondence</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">We receive and respond to all official communications from EU competent authorities on your behalf.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:folder" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Documentation Maintenance</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">We maintain and update required technical documentation, declarations of conformity, and registration records.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:bell" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Incident & Vigilance Reporting</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">We manage serious incident reporting and field safety corrective action notifications to EU authorities as required.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-slate-50 rounded-xl p-6 border border-slate-100">
          <Icon name="uil:sync" class="w-7 h-7 mb-3" style="color: #003399" />
          <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800 mb-2">Annual Review</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm">Yearly review of your regulatory status, any changes in EU law that affect your product, and updates to registration where needed.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-10 text-center">How It Works</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-6">
        <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
          <div class="text-white rounded-full w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0" style="background-color: #003399">1</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Initial Consultation (free)</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">We assess which regulation applies to your product, MDR, IVDR, EU AI Act, or a combination, and confirm what representation you need.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
          <div class="text-white rounded-full w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0" style="background-color: #003399">2</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Mandate & Agreement</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">We draft and sign the written mandate agreement. You receive a copy for your technical file and regulatory documentation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
          <div class="text-white rounded-full w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0" style="background-color: #003399">3</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Registration</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">We register as your EU Authorised Representative with the relevant authorities and provide you with the registration details for your product labelling and documentation.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="flex gap-5 items-start">
          <div class="text-white rounded-full w-9 h-9 flex items-center justify-center font-bold shrink-0" style="background-color: #003399">4</div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-semibold text-gray-800">Ongoing Representation</h3>
            <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-1">We remain your active EU representative, handling correspondence, monitoring regulatory changes, and keeping your registration current.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl mt-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800 mb-8 text-center">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
      <div class="flex flex-col gap-5">
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Who needs an EU Authorised Representative?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-4">Any company based outside the EU that places a regulated product on the EU market, including medical devices (MDR/IVDR) and high-risk AI systems under the EU AI Act, must designate an EU Authorised Representative.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            Does this cover the EU AI Act as well as MDR?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-4">Yes. We can act as your representative under MDR, IVDR, the EU AI Act, or all three depending on your product classification.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            What country are you registered in?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-4">AnichLabs OÜ is registered in Estonia, which is a full EU member state. Our registration satisfies the EU establishment requirement.</p>
        </details>
        <details class="bg-slate-50 border border-slate-100 rounded-xl p-6 group">
          <summary class="font-semibold text-gray-800 cursor-pointer list-none flex justify-between items-center">
            What happens if there is a regulatory issue?
            <Icon name="uil:angle-down" class="w-5 h-5 text-slate-400 group-open:rotate-180 transition-transform" />
          </summary>
          <p class="text-slate-500 text-sm mt-4">We handle all communication with EU authorities on your behalf. For serious issues we work with you and, where needed, specialist regulatory legal counsel.</p>
        </details>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl mt-20 mb-10 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-800">Ready to establish your EU presence?</h2>
      <p class="text-slate-500 mt-3">Book a free 30-minute call to confirm what representation your product requires and get a clear quote.</p>
      <a href="https://calendly.com/chris-anichlabs/30min" target="_blank" rel="noopener"
        class="mt-6 inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-white font-semibold px-6 py-3 rounded-lg transition-colors"
        style="background-color: #003399">
        <Icon name="uil:calendar-alt" class="w-5 h-5" />
        Book a Free Call
      </a>
    </div>

  </Container>
</Layout>
